==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stopping
<hw>Stop"ping</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Material
for filling a cavity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mining)</fld> <def>A partition or door to direct or
prevent a current of air.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Far.)</fld> <def>A pad or poultice of dung or other
material applied to a horse's hoof to keep it moist.</def>
<rj><au>Youatt.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stopping-out</ent>⟦br⟧
